# Document Types

## Form I-20

### Purpose

Form I-20 shows that a student has been admitted to an SEVP-certified school and is eligible to apply for F-1 or M-1 student status.

### Common Users

- International students
- F-1 students
- M-1 students

### Important Fields

- Student name
- SEVIS ID
- School name
- Program start date
- Program end date
- Education level
- Major/program
- Financial information
- Travel endorsement

### Common Confusions

- I-20 expiration vs visa expiration
- Travel signature validity
- SEVIS ID location
- Program end date meaning
- Difference between maintaining status and visa validity

