## Form I-766 / EAD

### Purpose

Form I-766, also called an Employment Authorization Document or EAD card, shows that a person is authorized to work in the United States for a specific period.

### Important Fields

- Cardholder name
- USCIS number
- Category
- Card number
- Valid from date
- Card expires date
- Terms and conditions

### Common Confusions

- EAD approval vs physical card
- OPT start date vs EAD valid-from date
- Whether work can begin before receiving the card
- Expiration date
- Employment category code